<i>adjective</i>: 연연하다 [여ː년하다], 엉거주춤하다 [엉거주춤하다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt>연연하다 [여ː년하다]</dt><br>
<dd>lingering; longed-for</dd><br>
<dd>매우 그립다.</dd><br>
<dd>Yearning for something or someone ardently.</dd><br>
<dt>엉거주춤하다 [엉거주춤하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. crooked; bent</dd><br>
<dd>앉은 것과 선 것의 중간 자세로, 몸을 반쯤 굽힌 상태이다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being in the posture in between sitting and standing, with the body bent halfway.</dd><br>
<dd>2. faltering; hovering; lingering</dd><br>
<dd>망설이며 머뭇거리는 상태이다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being in the state of wavering and hesitating.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>